{
  "name": "corpus-lite",
  "version": "1.0.5",
  "productName": "WordZ",
  "description": "一个本地桌面语料分析工具。",
  "main": "main.js",
  "packageManager": "npm@11.9.0",
  "scripts": {
    "start": "electron .",
    "build:assets": "node scripts/generate-build-assets.mjs",
    "pack": "npm run build:assets && electron-builder --dir --publish never",
    "dist": "npm run build:assets && electron-builder --publish never",
    "dist:mac": "npm run build:assets && electron-builder --mac --publish never",
    "dist:win": "npm run build:assets && electron-builder --win --x64 --publish never",
    "dist:win:arm64": "npm run build:assets && electron-builder --win --arm64 --publish never",
    "release:github": "npm run build:assets && node scripts/github-release.mjs",
    "release:github:mac": "npm run build:assets && node scripts/github-release.mjs --mac",
    "release:github:win": "npm run build:assets && node scripts/github-release.mjs --win --x64",
    "release:github:win:arm64": "npm run build:assets && node scripts/github-release.mjs --win --arm64",
    "release:notes": "node scripts/generate-release-notes.mjs",
    "release:doctor": "node scripts/release-doctor.mjs",
    "deps:check": "node scripts/dependency-health.mjs",
    "check:syntax": "node --check main.js && node --check autoUpdate.js && node --check corpusFileReader.js && node --check corpusStorage.js && node --check diagnostics.js && node --check preload.js && node --check renderer.js && node --check renderer/app.mjs && node --check renderer/constants.mjs && node --check renderer/domRefs.mjs && node --check renderer/utils.mjs && node --check renderer/feedback.mjs && node --check renderer/analysisBridge.mjs && node --check renderer/tableRender.mjs && node --check renderer/uiSettings.mjs && node --check renderer/features/stats.mjs && node --check renderer/features/compare.mjs && node --check renderer/features/kwic.mjs && node --check renderer/features/collocate.mjs && node --check renderer/features/library.mjs && node --check renderer/features/locator.mjs && node --check analysisCore.mjs && node --check analysisWorker.mjs && node --check smoke/electron.smoke.mjs && node --check scripts/dependency-health.mjs && node --check scripts/github-release.mjs && node --check scripts/generate-build-assets.mjs && node --check scripts/generate-release-notes.mjs && node --check scripts/release-doctor.mjs",
    "test": "node --test",
    "test:smoke": "node --test smoke/electron.smoke.mjs",
    "verify": "npm run check:syntax && npm test",
    "verify:smoke": "npm run verify && npm run test:smoke"
  },
  "author": "邹羽轩",
  "wordz": {
    "help": [
      "使用“打开语料”菜单可快速打开 txt / docx / pdf，或导入并保存到本地语料库。",
      "使用“本地语料库”可以按分类管理语料，也可以恢复、修复或从回收站找回误删内容。",
      "先点击“开始统计”，再进行 KWIC、Collocate 和原文定位查看，会得到更完整的分析结果。",
      "建议定期使用“备份语料库”创建外部备份；如果目录异常，可使用“修复语料库”检查并隔离坏数据。",
      "自动更新默认走 GitHub Releases；使用 GitHub Actions 发布工作流时，会自动把当前仓库 owner/repo 注入到打包结果里。"
    ],
    "autoUpdate": {
      "enabled": true,
      "provider": "github",
      "channel": "latest",
      "checkOnLaunch": true,
      "autoDownload": true,
      "allowPrerelease": false,
      "checkDelayMs": 12000,
      "github": {
        "owner": "",
        "repo": "",
        "private": false
      }
    },
    "release": {
      "channel": "stable"
    },
    "releaseNotes": [
      "修复 macOS DMG 的许可文案编码问题：简体中文许可文件现在使用更明确的 zh_CN 命名，不再被 DMG 构建流程误判为繁体中文编码。",
      "保持 Windows 安装器中文许可与发布体检同步更新，稳定版打包配置在 macOS 和 Windows 上更一致。",
      "继续保持 stable 单渠道发布策略，兼容现有自动更新与 GitHub Releases 发布流程。"
    ]
  },
  "license": "MIT",
  "homepage": "https://github.com/zzwdh/WordZ",
  "bugs": {
    "url": "https://github.com/zzwdh/WordZ/issues"
  },
  "repository": {
    "type": "git",
    "url": "https://github.com/zzwdh/WordZ.git"
  },
  "engines": {
    "node": ">=24.14.0 <25",
    "npm": ">=11 <12"
  },
  "build": {
    "appId": "com.zzwdh.wordz",
    "productName": "WordZ",
    "artifactName": "${productName}-${version}-${os}-${arch}.${ext}",
    "copyright": "Copyright © 2026 邹羽轩",
    "directories": {
      "output": "dist",
      "buildResources": "build"
    },
    "files": [
      "**/*",
      "!dist{,/**}",
      "!out{,/**}",
      "!coverage{,/**}",
      "!smoke{,/**}",
      "!test{,/**}",
      "!.git{,/**}",
      "!.DS_Store",
      "!*.log"
    ],
    "asar": true,
    "npmRebuild": false,
    "mac": {
      "icon": "build/icon.icns",
      "category": "public.app-category.productivity",
      "hardenedRuntime": true,
      "gatekeeperAssess": false,
      "entitlements": "build/entitlements.mac.plist",
      "entitlementsInherit": "build/entitlements.mac.inherit.plist",
      "target": [
        "dmg",
        "zip"
      ]
    },
    "dmg": {
      "icon": "build/icon.icns",
      "title": "${productName} ${version}",
      "contents": [
        {
          "x": 156,
          "y": 214
        },
        {
          "x": 414,
          "y": 214,
          "type": "link",
          "path": "/Applications"
        }
      ]
    },
    "win": {
      "icon": "build/icon.ico",
      "legalTrademarks": "WordZ · 邹羽轩",
      "requestedExecutionLevel": "asInvoker",
      "target": [
        "nsis",
        "zip"
      ]
    },
    "nsis": {
      "oneClick": false,
      "allowToChangeInstallationDirectory": true,
      "createDesktopShortcut": "always",
      "createStartMenuShortcut": true,
      "runAfterFinish": true,
      "menuCategory": true,
      "deleteAppDataOnUninstall": false,
      "displayLanguageSelector": false,
      "shortcutName": "WordZ",
      "uninstallDisplayName": "WordZ",
      "installerIcon": "build/icon.ico",
      "uninstallerIcon": "build/icon.ico",
      "installerHeaderIcon": "build/icon.ico",
      "installerSidebar": "build/installer-sidebar.bmp",
      "uninstallerSidebar": "build/installer-sidebar.bmp",
      "installerHeader": "build/installer-header.bmp",
      "license": "build/license_zh_CN.txt"
    },
    "publish": [
      {
        "provider": "github",
        "releaseType": "release"
      }
    ]
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "electron": "^41.0.3",
    "electron-builder": "^26.8.1",
    "playwright-core": "^1.58.2"
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "electron-updater": "^6.8.3",
    "exceljs": "^4.4.0",
    "iconv-lite": "^0.7.2",
    "mammoth": "^1.12.0",
    "pdf-parse": "^2.4.5"
  }
}
